teal.physics.em

Interface GeneratesE

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Circuit, Coil, ConductingSphericalShell, ConstantField, CoulombsLaw.UniformEField, CurrentSlab, CylindricalField, CylindricalMagnet, Dipole, ElectricDipole, EMRadiator, FiniteWire, GenericEField, HollowCurrentShell, InfiniteConductingPlane, InfiniteLineCharge, InfiniteWire, LineMagneticDipole, MagneticDipole, PointCharge, PointChargeConductingSphere, RingOfCurrent

    public interface GeneratesE
    Objects that generate a Electric field should implement GeneratesE. When a World responds to getE requests, it will only sum up the electric fields of GeneratesE objects.
